1
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:40,960
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:43,759
Xiaolan,

3
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,200
did you have fun

4
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:45,840
on this trip?

5
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,509
Yes, I did.

6
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,560
You did?

7
00:01:47,870 --> 00:01:48,870
Then let's go out every year

8
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:49,560
from now on,

9
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:50,120
okay?

10
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:50,840
Okay.

11
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:53,050
Then, Xiaolan, you decide

12
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,720
where we should go next time.

13
00:01:59,570 --> 00:02:02,350
[Episode 13: The Piercing Sound of Brakes]

14
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:08,919
You're up.

15
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:10,630
Did you sleep well upstairs?

16
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,420
Where is Cheng?

17
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,520
Look at the time.

18
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,750
He's gone to work.

19
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:19,470
What was that word again?

20
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,430
The "white"...

21
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:21,570
White-collar.

22
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:22,710
Right.

23
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,800
Well, look—

24
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,960
you just sit in an office all day
pushing paper,

25
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:28,240
and they dress it up with a fancy name:
white-collar.

26
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,800
Kang Wei.

27
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,910
Don't forget what you said

28
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,680
last night.

29
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,150
A young idler,

30
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:34,310
an old beggar.

31
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:34,820
I'm off.

32
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,180
Yeah, yeah, got it.

33
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,890
Aren't you going to open one for me?

34
00:02:42,890 --> 00:02:44,940
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

35
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:45,800
I'm going out for a bit

36
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,660
to see a client.

37
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:49,800
Morning, Cheng.

38
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:50,310
Morning.

39
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,000
Had breakfast?

40
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,470
Yeah.

41
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:52,120
Alright.

42
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,250
Zhou Cheng,

43
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,910
if there's something you want to do,

44
00:02:58,910 --> 00:02:59,710
just go for it.

45
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:01,170
Go fight for it.

46
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,680
We may be young,

47
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,020
but we're just as capable.

48
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:14,820
Senior.

49
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:22,800
Um...

50
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,540
I want to take on a case.

51
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,490
You want to take on a case already?

52
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,280
I know

53
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,010
I haven't been at the firm long,

54
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,250
but I also remember,

55
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,020
right here in this office,

56
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:39,280
you said young people
should push themselves,

57
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,079
take chances,

58
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,820
break free from some rules
and constraints,

59
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,240
and do what they want.

60
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,590
So you're breaking the rules

61
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:47,050
and coming to me for a case?

62
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:48,800
Yes.

63
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:50,560
But I've finished going through

64
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,620
all the case files,

65
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:53,430
I'm familiar with how the firm works,

66
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,870
and I've helped a lot of other lawyers

67
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,240
with prep work.

68
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,000
I think I'm ready

69
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,290
to take on a case.

70
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,360
I could tell long ago

71
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,840
that you couldn't hold back anymore.

72
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,840
I was wondering how long you could
hold yourself back.

73
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:09,400
Here. This one's yours.

74
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,930
[Investigation Report
on the Radio Smuggling Case]

75
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,090
Smuggling?

76
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:14,710
Yes.

77
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,040
You can take Shi Kai

78
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,370
and work on it together.

79
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:19,829
This batch of smuggled goods

80
00:04:19,829 --> 00:04:20,870
was found

81
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:21,890
at a fisherman's home.

82
00:04:21,890 --> 00:04:22,920
But the fisherman insists

83
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,450
they fished it out of the sea

84
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,410
and didn't know it was contraband.

85
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,190
But it's a large batch.

86
00:04:29,650 --> 00:04:31,000
Even if they didn't know it was smuggled,

87
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,150
it's still of unknown origin.

88
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:33,750
They shouldn't have kept it.

89
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,630
Fishermen aren't educated

90
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:36,890
and don't know the law.

91
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,870
They probably just wanted to
make some money.

92
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,080
That's not the same as smuggling.

93
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,040
We still need to hear

94
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,870
both sides.

95
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,870
How much longer are you two going to
mope around?

96
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,310
It was just one setback.

97
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,680
One of you is a boss,

98
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,950
and the other negotiates business deals—

99
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:51,480
and look at yourselves now.

100
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,920
I got you changed into these clothes,

101
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,480
hoping to make you feel refreshed

102
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,430
and start anew.

103
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,659
Look at you two—

104
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:57,240
do you even look like

105
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,500
you want to start over?

106
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,160
Kang Wei!

107
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:01,360
Zhenzhu!

108
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,190
Young people should be full of vitality,

109
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:04,800
you know?

110
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:06,430
Full of energy!

111
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:07,610
Look at you two!

112
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:08,070
I...

113
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:12,670
What's wrong?

114
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,870
Look at the two of you.

115
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:19,070
No matter how beautiful the clothes are,

116
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,270
they look lifeless

117
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,510
on you.

118
00:05:21,550 --> 00:05:22,430
Exactly!

119
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,830
Right now, you've got no spark!

120
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:27,600
No energy, no confidence.

121
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,050
Even the nicest clothes

122
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,720
lose their value

123
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,750
when worn

124
00:05:31,770 --> 00:05:33,010
by you!

125
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,360
Granny Yu,

126
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:38,840
you've seen the world
and have a sharp eye.

127
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,920
Could you do us the honor

128
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,659
of giving them some pointers?

129
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,600
Look at you two.

130
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:49,270
Are you still a girl?

131
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,409
Look at the way you're sitting.

132
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,190
Do girls sit like that?

133
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:55,050
With your legs spread so wide?

134
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,270
And you,

135
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,510
a young man, should have energy.

136
00:05:58,510 --> 00:05:59,770
You need to look sharp!

137
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,000
Stand up!

138
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,000
A person,

139
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,670
no matter the situation,

140
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,950
should never slouch or hunch over.

141
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,600
Chin up

142
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:13,920
and chest out.

143
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,070
Lift your head!

144
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,270
That's more like it.

145
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,720
You're in business now.

146
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:21,190
You need to

147
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,920
be conscious of your image at all times.

148
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,510
Exactly.

149
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,360
Granny Yu is right.

150
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,870
When we're out in the world,

151
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,720
we create our own persona.

152
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,510
We must have a sense of conviction.

153
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:32,600
-What... What persona? Sense of what?
-What are you talking about?

154
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,260
Never mind.

155
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:35,040
Just listen carefully to Granny Yu.

156
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,640
Granny Yu,

157
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,920
please continue.

158
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:40,120
-Please give us some advice, Granny Yu!
-Please give us some advice, Granny Yu!

159
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,159
That's better.

160
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:43,070
Success

161
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:43,750
is never easy.

162
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,159
You have to consider
not only the brightness of the lamp

163
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:47,120
but also its color temperature

164
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,680
and frequency.

165
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,190
Your child studies for long hours,

166
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:50,720
so buying a good lamp

167
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:51,870
can help

168
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,040
protect your child's eyesight.

169
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,600
Ms. Bai,

170
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,950
it's a pleasure doing business with you!

171
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,000
May we grow big and strong together

172
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,040
and prosper as one!

173
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,120
Let's get rich together.

174
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,320
It's fine. It's fine.

175
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,190
Take care!

176
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:07,560
Look over here! Over here!

177
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,600
Granny Yu, let's take a photo together!

178
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,160
Come on, Granny Yu!

179
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:11,120
[A Natural Healer]

180
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,190
Just one photo! Just one!

181
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,830
Granny Yu, just one. Come on!

182
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,510
Two!

183
00:07:12,510 --> 00:07:12,920
Xiaolan.

184
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,270
No!

185
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:13,720
One!

186
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,040
Alright, alright, alright!

187
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,270
Hold the flowers, Granny Yu.

188
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:17,720
Okay.

189
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,000
Here!

190
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:22,280
-Thank you, Granny Yu!
-Thank you, Granny Yu!

191
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,950
"A natural healer?"

192
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,920
I'm not a doctor.

193
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,310
Oh, come on.

194
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,130
Granny Yu,

195
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,430
you're the doctor of our souls,

196
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,800
a healer of our bearing!

197
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,830
With your guidance,

198
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:36,120
I feel like
I've been improving rapidly lately,

199
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,800
and I'm now at
the starting line of success!

200
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:40,480
The starting line!

201
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,280
That's right!

202
00:07:42,690 --> 00:07:44,040
You've only just reached

203
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,560
the starting line of success?

204
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,920
Then you'd better start crawling your way

205
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,159
up that road.

206
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,010
Granny Yu, don't go just yet.

207
00:07:51,010 --> 00:07:52,430
We have one more big gift for you.

208
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:52,950
Look!

209
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,920
We've carefully chosen

210
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,310
a chandelier for you.

211
00:07:58,390 --> 00:08:00,240
It suits your elegance perfectly.

212
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,120
Let us install it for you!

213
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:01,600
Hold on.

214
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,430
Granny Yu has her rules—

215
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,400
no one enters her room casually.

216
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:06,830
Granny Yu,

217
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,950
what do you think?

218
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,560
Could you let them

219
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,120
show their appreciation?

220
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,240
Alright, go ahead, go ahead.

221
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,310
-Okay!
-Got it!

222
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,440
Here, let me take it.

223
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,090
I'll open the door for you.

224
00:08:20,950 --> 00:08:22,270
But don't hang
that "A Natural Healer" banner

225
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,240
for me.

226
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,310
Okay. Hang it over the bed!

227
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:24,970
Okay, okay!

228
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:31,830
Granny Yu,

229
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,440
there's something

230
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,039
I'd like to discuss with you.

231
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:38,080
What are you up to this time?

232
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,150
Granny Yu,

233
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:43,200
I'd like to ask you to help train

234
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,260
Luna's employees.

235
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:45,600
Don't worry.

236
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:47,000
You won't be doing it for free.

237
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,270
I'll pay you

238
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,360
according to Luna's

239
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,560
HR salary standards.

240
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:53,670
Nowadays, there are
white-collar workers everywhere,

241
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:55,390
and so many college graduates too.

242
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:56,630
I'm just an old woman.

243
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,720
I can't handle that kind of work.

244
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,480
Granny Yu,

245
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:00,240
look.

246
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:02,240
You even know what "white-collar" means.

247
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,500
You're so up-to-date,

248
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:04,750
so don't be so modest.

249
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,550
What I'm building this time

250
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:09,080
is the first nationally branded store
of its kind.

251
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:09,960
The staff inside

252
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,870
must be distinguished from

253
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,390
those in small, ordinary shops.

254
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:15,270
I've thought it over,

255
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,510
and only you, Granny Yu,

256
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:17,870
can handle this job.

257
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,410
You come from a prestigious family

258
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:21,600
with

259
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,910
stores in the city

260
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,390
and businesses across Southeast Asia.

261
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:26,030
A woman like you

262
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,400
has seen everything.

263
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:28,510
Besides,

264
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,030
you're highly respected

265
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:30,960
and naturally authoritative.

266
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,790
Those young people

267
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,290
will listen to you
the moment they see you.

268
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,550
Alright.

269
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,080
I'll train those girls

270
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,030
of yours

271
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,440
to be just like you—

272
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,790
when they open their mouths,

273
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:46,670
they make everyone feel like
they're in full bloom.

274
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,040
Thank you, Granny Yu.

275
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,270
When do you open?

276
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,200
Everything is ready.

277
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,840
We're just waiting for the final piece.

278
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,170
I'm your "final piece"?

279
00:09:58,110 --> 00:09:58,660
Yes!

280
00:09:58,930 --> 00:10:00,280
[Luna]

281
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,600
Ms. Xia,

282
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,390
this "final piece" you want

283
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,650
is nearly impossible!

284
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,080
Getting performers
for the Chinese New Year Gala

285
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,390
to wear our brand...

286
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:09,160
You really do dare to dream.

287
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,360
Mr. Chen,

288
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,960
you've moved to Shengcheng.

289
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,270
You've basically burned your bridges
to go all in.

290
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:15,400
Surely, you have the fighting spirit.

291
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:15,910
Fine.

292
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,440
You dare to dream it,
and I dare to make it happen!

293
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,640
Alright, let's do it!

294
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,320
But can we

295
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,000
replace the sign by the door first?

296
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,030
That sign looks far too shabby.

297
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,080
Okay, okay. Soon.

298
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,270
The new one will be ready next week.

299
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:26,270
With large gold-embossed letters!

300
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:33,940
It's m-my wife.

301
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,030
I'm stepping out to make a call.

302
00:10:35,030 --> 00:10:36,360
You go ahead and look around yourself.

303
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,000
You should get a brick phone!

304
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,200
I'll buy one once the company opens!

305
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:44,440
Luna—

306
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,640
the first domestic women's fashion brand.

307
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,910
Built from nothing, it rose to glory,

308
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,960
then fell into decline.

309
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,840
And Chen Xiliang

310
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:56,240
reached the peak of his life
because of Luna

311
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:58,670
but also lost his life because of it.

312
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,910
I used to be the most

313
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,750
overlooked salesperson at Luna.

314
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:03,390
Now,

315
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,550
right here,

316
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,910
I'm going to get everything I once desired

317
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:08,550
but was too afraid to pursue.

318
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:15,750
Ms. Xia.

319
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,630
Is something wrong at home?

320
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:20,600
It's nothing really.

321
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,390
My wife...

322
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,320
heard I was moving to Shengcheng.

323
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,080
She's unhappy,

324
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,510
so she's finding excuses to pick a fight.

325
00:11:25,510 --> 00:11:26,360
You came to Shengcheng

326
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,390
to hide from your family, didn't you?

327
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,480
The two of us...

328
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:30,110
Well,

329
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,200
our families arranged for us to meet.

330
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,120
We didn't have any feelings for each other
to begin with.

331
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:34,750
Later,

332
00:11:35,030 --> 00:11:36,750
her brother got into gambling.

333
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:37,680
Then, every day,

334
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:40,080
her family pressured her
to ask me for money.

335
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,750
Anyway, let's not talk about that.

336
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,510
Right now, I only have one thing
on my mind—

337
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:45,150
building Luna into something great.

338
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:45,610
Come on,

339
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:47,050
let me show you around.

340
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:50,690
Mr. Tang,

341
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,240
you really didn't have to come with me.

342
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:52,750
Look,

343
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,320
t-the market is so chaotic.

344
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,120
It's not chaotic at all.

345
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,030
It's bustling!

346
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,670
So lively, so vibrant!

347
00:11:58,550 --> 00:11:59,750
Excuse me! Excuse me!

348
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:00,600
Excuse me, coming through!

349
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,200
Watch out!

350
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,750
Thanks, thanks! Sorry about that!

351
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:03,550
Excuse me!

352
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,550
Let me take a look?

353
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:29,080
No need. It's nothing.

354
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,680
Let me see.

355
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:37,430
It's your zodiac year this year?

356
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,150
No.

357
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:40,600
Well...

358
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,580
Let's buy you a new outfit to change into.

359
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,270
Well...

360
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:48,550
Good thing we're in a clothing market.

361
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:50,950
Otherwise, I wouldn't know
how to fix this.

362
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:52,440
Here.

363
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:53,550
Cover it with my bag.

364
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,210
Okay, okay.

365
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,080
You go ahead, and I'll follow.

366
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,480
Okay.

367
00:12:59,390 --> 00:12:59,840
This way.

368
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,440
Well, this is embarrassing.

369
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,550
I've never worn clothes

370
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,240
quite like this before.

371
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:09,910
Do I look okay?

372
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:11,310
Yeah, you look very nice.

373
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,040
Very nice.

374
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,670
It makes you give off
a completely different vibe.

375
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:17,180
Do I look like a businessman now?

376
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:17,840
Maybe I should just join you

377
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,040
and go into business.

378
00:13:21,450 --> 00:13:22,360
Once you put the outfit on,

379
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,690
you look years younger.

380
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:24,550
Sir,

381
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,510
your wife

382
00:13:25,510 --> 00:13:27,370
has excellent taste in clothing.

383
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,080
Very good.

384
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,200
Careful.

385
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,330
Thank you for today.

386
00:13:46,270 --> 00:13:47,600
Why are you thanking me?

387
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,670
If anything,

388
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:49,870
I should be thanking you.

389
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,000
Otherwise, well...

390
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,570
I would've embarrassed myself again.

391
00:13:53,750 --> 00:13:55,080
Let's not stand on ceremony between us—

392
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,870
we're just helping each other out.

393
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:57,930
Um, your collar...

394
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,150
Collar.

395
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,040
Well, I...

396
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,720
I've never worn clothes like this before.

397
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,110
I'll head back now.

398
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:09,320
Okay.

399
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:10,560
Goodbye.

400
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:11,200
Goodbye.

401
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:15,670
Bye-bye.

402
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,040
Bye.

403
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,010
Let's go.

404
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,450
Big cities are just on another level.

405
00:14:32,450 --> 00:14:33,930
The styles, the fabrics,

406
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,000
and the colors—

407
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,150
they're so trendy

408
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:37,150
and very stylish.

409
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:39,240
I've written down the numbers

410
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,320
of all those stalls.

411
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:40,960
I'm here!

412
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:42,630
Uncle, you're here.

413
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:43,030
Yong!

414
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:48,790
Have some water.

415
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:49,360
Uncle.

416
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:52,270
The bidding documents are ready?

417
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:52,910
All set.

418
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:56,180
I've brought
both the originals and copies.

419
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:57,770
[Yuanhui Decoration Bidding Documents]

420
00:14:59,360 --> 00:14:59,910
Fen.

421
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:01,030
You're dressed so nicely.

422
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:02,160
Where have you been?

423
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:03,550
Really?

424
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:06,670
I went to... do some market research.

425
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:09,240
The format looks fine.

426
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,320
Whether Yuanhui

427
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:12,240
can make a name for itself in Shengcheng

428
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,370
depends on this bid.

429
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,860
I'll go over it carefully again tonight.

430
00:15:22,250 --> 00:15:23,630
Didn't Uncle say we'd go together?

431
00:15:23,630 --> 00:15:24,770
Why aren't they here yet?

432
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:26,200
Chengzi said he'd come by himself,

433
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:26,910
but early this morning,

434
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:28,570
he got called to meet a client.

435
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:42,080
Kang Wei?

436
00:15:54,870 --> 00:15:55,530
Don't move!

437
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:56,620
Don't move!

438
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:03,650
Kang Wei.

439
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,840
Quick, take my car
and drive Xiaolan there.

440
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,170
Okay.

441
00:16:06,250 --> 00:16:07,360
I'll take this guy to the police station.

442
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,360
Behave yourself!

443
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:08,960
Uncle,

444
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:09,810
are you sure you can handle this alone?

445
00:16:09,810 --> 00:16:11,510
Handling this punk? No problem.

446
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:12,170
Let go of me.

447
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:13,000
Xiaolan!

448
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:13,910
Behave!

449
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:25,790
Hello.

450
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:26,880
-I'm here to submit the bidding documents.
-Hello.

451
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:27,720
Submitting a bid, right?

452
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:28,030
Yes.

453
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:28,910
Just put it over there.

454
00:16:28,910 --> 00:16:30,240
Come on, register here.

455
00:16:34,450 --> 00:16:35,170
[Shengcheng Yuanhui Decoration Co., Ltd.;]

456
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:35,890
[Shengcheng Guesthouse Renovation Project]
[Bid Document]

457
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:37,440
[Shengcheng Guesthouse; Bidding Office]

458
00:16:38,270 --> 00:16:38,960
Xiaolan,

459
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:39,920
that was fast.

460
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,320
Just submitting the bid.
What more did you expect?

461
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,610
Going in and sitting for a while for tea?

462
00:16:43,610 --> 00:16:45,150
I didn't think it would be that simple.

463
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:45,900
After all, this bid

464
00:16:45,900 --> 00:16:47,320
determines Yuanhui's future development.

465
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:49,270
I thought it would be
more of a grand occasion.

466
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:51,150
Many life-changing events

467
00:16:51,390 --> 00:16:53,510
happen without you even realizing it.

468
00:16:53,510 --> 00:16:54,040
Let's go.

469
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:02,720
Xiaolan,

470
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:04,240
why did Ke Yixiong's man

471
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,960
try to snatch our bidding documents?

472
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,069
Liu Tianquan is the one behind this.

473
00:17:07,069 --> 00:17:08,970
Ke Yixiong's man just did it for money.

474
00:17:08,970 --> 00:17:10,440
Liu Tianquan approached Uncle before,

475
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,770
wanting to rig the bid with him.

476
00:17:11,770 --> 00:17:13,790
He offered money for us to throw the bid.

477
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:15,480
No way Uncle Yong would agree to that.

478
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,640
Just throwing them out
without roughing them up

479
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,109
would have been letting them off easy.

480
00:17:18,109 --> 00:17:19,310
Uncle indeed didn't let them off easy—

481
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:20,839
he drove them out directly.

482
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:25,109
I told you to let her have the bid,
and you went behind my back to rig it?

483
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:25,680
Do you even know

484
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,750
that I'm your young master?

485
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:27,750
You darn bastard!

486
00:17:28,069 --> 00:17:28,750
Drive faster!

487
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:29,110
Yes.

488
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:30,920
Xia Xiaolan is submitting the bid today.

489
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,000
I need to go explain everything to her.

490
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,400
It's fine, Young Master.

491
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:35,840
You don't have to get so angry, actually.

492
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,030
A car!

493
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,020
A car is coming!

494
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:48,400
Watch out!

495
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,090
Young Master...

496
00:18:50,510 --> 00:18:51,440
Are you alright?

497
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:28,380
Kang Wei...

498
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:30,690
Kang Wei?

499
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:31,590
Kang Wei!

500
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,400
Kang Wei! Kang Wei!

501
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:41,460
Xia Xiaolan's car...

502
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:43,490
It's Xia Xiaolan's car!

503
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:50,510
Help!

504
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:51,520
Please help!

505
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,720
-Xia Xiaolan!
-Ms. Xia!

506
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:54,120
Are you alright, Ms. Xia?

507
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:00,520
Kang Wei! Kang Wei!

508
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,030
Let's go!

509
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:01,760
Xia Xiaolan.

510
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:02,440
Get out of the car.

511
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:03,200
Get out! It's dangerous!

512
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:03,880
Let go of me!

513
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,000
Get out! It's dangerous!

514
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:05,400
Kang Wei!

515
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,400
Get out first!

516
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:07,920
Get out of the car first!

517
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:09,480
Du Zhaohui,

518
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,480
are you satisfied now?

519
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:11,510
What are you talking about?

520
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,030
Come on, let's go to the hospital!

521
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:13,200
I need to save Kang Wei!

522
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:13,920
You guys go ahead!

523
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,300
Kang Wei! I need to save Kang Wei!

524
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:16,390
I'll save Kang Wei!

525
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,030
Let go of me!

526
00:20:18,030 --> 00:20:19,070
Come on! Let's go to the hospital!

527
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:19,880
I need to save Kang Wei!

528
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,640
Kang Wei!

529
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,440
Let's go! To the hospital first!

530
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,200
Come on!

531
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:27,110
Wake up, man!

532
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,110
Don't sleep!

533
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,270
Don't fall asleep!

534
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,640
Someone, help!

535
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,410
Get him out of the car! Help!

536
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:38,370
Be careful, nurse.

537
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:40,840
Make sure she doesn't get any scars, okay?

538
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,550
Xia Xiaolan, let's go to the ER.

539
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,270
As for Mr. Kang,

540
00:20:47,270 --> 00:20:47,750
I will...

541
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:48,410
Du Zhaohui,

542
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,400
can you stay away from me?

543
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,120
I'll say it one more time:

544
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:53,720
if anything happens to Kang Wei,

545
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:55,780
no amount of money will make up for it!

546
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,030
I know that.

547
00:20:57,070 --> 00:20:57,790
As for Mr. Kang,

548
00:20:57,790 --> 00:20:58,880
I'll take full responsibility.

549
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,340
And for you, I will also...

550
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:05,270
First, you tried to
snatch our bidding documents,

551
00:21:05,270 --> 00:21:06,600
then you rammed into us—

552
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:07,440
Du Zhaohui,

553
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,440
is this how you "build" Shengcheng?

554
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:11,200
It's just a guesthouse project.

555
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,480
Did you really have to bring

556
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:13,640
your family's tactics here?

557
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,570
I'm telling you,

558
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:15,830
this is Shengcheng!

559
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,090
We follow the law here!

560
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:17,960
It's all my fault.

561
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:18,920
It's a misunderstanding!

562
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:19,830
As for the guesthouse project,

563
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:20,680
I already told Liu Tianquan

564
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:21,680
to let you have it!

565
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,720
I knew you were submitting the bid today.

566
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,920
I just wanted to ask you out
for afternoon tea.

567
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,920
I like you so much.

568
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:28,400
How could I have hurt you?

569
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,830
You darn scumbag!

570
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:33,480
Driving like a maniac!

571
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,680
How dare you kick my Young Master?

572
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:37,510
Why did you hit my Young Master?

573
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:39,440
One more word and I'll kick you too!

574
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:42,200
Y-Young Master.

575
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:44,110
Is that your tooth?

576
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:44,790
My tooth!

577
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:47,200
It really is your tooth!

578
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,030
My tooth!

579
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,340
I need a doctor.

580
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,510
I need to be hospitalized!

581
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,400
You barbarian!

582
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:53,070
Doctor!

583
00:21:53,270 --> 00:21:53,960
Doctor! Doctor!

584
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:54,790
Any doctor?

585
00:21:55,010 --> 00:21:55,960
Did I say you could leave?

586
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:56,590
Zhenzhu.

587
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,540
I'll beat you every time I see you!

588
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,240
Calm down.

589
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:13,680
The surgery went very well.

590
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:14,270
He sustained

591
00:22:14,270 --> 00:22:15,600
a severe blow to the head

592
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,770
and fractured ribs.

593
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,160
He'll need time to recover.

594
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,110
Once the anesthesia wears off,

595
00:22:19,110 --> 00:22:20,640
he could wake up at any time.

596
00:22:22,590 --> 00:22:23,650
Thank you, doctor.

597
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:28,960
Are you alright?

598
00:22:38,110 --> 00:22:38,910
Young Master!

599
00:22:40,530 --> 00:22:41,610
Mr. Kang's surgery

600
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,920
is finished.

601
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,920
The doctor said it was a success.

602
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,350
He should wake up in a few days.

603
00:22:46,350 --> 00:22:47,510
And as for Ms. Xia,

604
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:48,440
she's been examined—

605
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,310
only superficial wounds,

606
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,270
no broken bones.

607
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:51,000
Really?

608
00:22:52,590 --> 00:22:53,790
The woman I fancy

609
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:55,650
sure is blessed with good fortune.

610
00:22:55,650 --> 00:22:57,060
Of course.

611
00:22:58,830 --> 00:23:00,400
What's all that fuss
over her bidding documents?

612
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:02,110
Young Master, you guessed right.

613
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:03,030
It was Liu Tianquan

614
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,490
who got Ke Yixiong to do it.

615
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,110
That bastard.

616
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,340
I told him to throw the bid,

617
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,480
and he actually dared to go against me.

618
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:11,000
He's nothing but

619
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,240
a lapdog to my father.

620
00:23:12,590 --> 00:23:14,640
If I hadn't taken a liking to his sister,

621
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:16,040
he'd have been long gone.

622
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:17,310
Call him here.

623
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:18,720
I want to knock out

624
00:23:18,830 --> 00:23:20,880
all his teeth right in front of Ms. Xia!

625
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,550
No problem.

626
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:23,440
But that bastard said

627
00:23:23,510 --> 00:23:26,550
something urgent came up with the group
and ran off long ago!

628
00:23:26,550 --> 00:23:28,280
Young Master, have some water.

629
00:23:28,770 --> 00:23:30,000
Not the sharpest tool,

630
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:31,060
but he sure can run.

631
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:33,640
Does he think my old man
will cover for him?

632
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:34,240
Fine.

633
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:36,120
Add his teeth to his debt.

634
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:36,880
Got it.

635
00:23:36,970 --> 00:23:37,830
I'll settle it with him when we get back.

636
00:23:37,830 --> 00:23:38,400
For sure.

637
00:23:40,270 --> 00:23:41,480
When a woman is injured,

638
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,880
she's at her most vulnerable—

639
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:44,200
most in need of someone to comfort her.

640
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,070
Exactly.

641
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:47,450
Has that Jerk Zhou shown up yet?

642
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:47,960
Zhou?

643
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:51,370
He's not here!

644
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,730
He's still not here yet!

645
00:23:53,510 --> 00:23:54,510
He didn't rush here the moment he heard?

646
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:55,070
Yeah.

647
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:57,770
Are they having a fight?

648
00:23:57,790 --> 00:23:59,030
Must be, I think.

649
00:23:59,270 --> 00:23:59,830
Great.

650
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:01,880
Flowers, fruit,

651
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:02,830
and food from some restaurant—

652
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,510
have it all sent to Ms. Xia's ward.

653
00:24:04,510 --> 00:24:05,510
Consider it done!

654
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,250
Be thorough.

655
00:24:06,310 --> 00:24:07,440
Prepare a set for Mr. Kang too.

656
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:07,880
Got it.

657
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:09,530
I'll go arrange it now.

658
00:24:10,550 --> 00:24:12,280
Young Master is so thoughtful.

659
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:14,120
Forgot to grab my jacket.

660
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:19,750
Why did the client

661
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,550
choose a place like this to meet?

662
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:37,550
This should be it.

663
00:24:38,040 --> 00:24:38,830
I'll take a look over there.

664
00:24:38,830 --> 00:24:39,830
Okay, be careful.

665
00:24:43,830 --> 00:24:44,490
Zhou Cheng!

666
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:01,310
Xiaolan?

667
00:25:01,890 --> 00:25:02,790
You look so pale.

668
00:25:02,790 --> 00:25:04,250
Let me get a doctor for you!

669
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,210
I'm fine.

670
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:06,960
No need.

671
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,920
I just had a bad dream.

672
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:11,000
Is Zhou Cheng here yet?

673
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:11,640
Not yet.

674
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:13,200
I've already paged him.

675
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:14,030
The law firm said

676
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:15,360
he went to meet a client.

677
00:25:15,510 --> 00:25:16,770
He should be here soon.

678
00:25:18,270 --> 00:25:19,720
How could this happen?

679
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,780
No matter the cost,

680
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:23,240
we have to make sure Kang Wei recovers!

681
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:24,040
I understand.

682
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:25,160
Kang Wei will be fine.

683
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:25,820
Where is he?

684
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:27,690
Xiaolan.

685
00:25:28,350 --> 00:25:29,010
How are you?

686
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:30,110
I'm fine.

687
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:31,350
How is Kang Wei?

688
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:34,970
Kang Wei... he hasn't woken up yet.

689
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,920
W-Who are you?

690
00:25:38,350 --> 00:25:39,330
I'm Xia Xiaolan.

691
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,000
I was at the scene

692
00:25:41,110 --> 00:25:42,440
when the accident happened.

693
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,300
You were there?

694
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:45,140
Tell us what happened!

695
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:53,350
Have you looked into

696
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:54,240
that Kang fellow?

697
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,400
Yes, Young Master.

698
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:56,480
That Kang Wei

699
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,080
is a friend of that Jerk Zhou.

700
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,030
From the Jingcheng.

701
00:25:59,030 --> 00:26:00,270
He ran a stall at Renmin Bridge.

702
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:01,680
His father was a soldier

703
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:02,920
who died

704
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:03,880
before he was born.

705
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,920
Now his second uncle looks after him.

706
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:07,640
His second uncle is Kang Lianming.

707
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,550
That man is very mysterious, Young Master.

708
00:26:09,550 --> 00:26:10,750
I couldn't find any info on him.

709
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,880
No idea what he does.

710
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:15,760
Not an ordinary person, indeed.

711
00:26:17,550 --> 00:26:18,680
Xia Xiaolan was

712
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,580
actually warning me earlier.

713
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,310
She does care about me, after all.

714
00:26:24,310 --> 00:26:27,310
I was thinking—could it be

715
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,500
that Ms. Xia was threatening you?

716
00:26:30,110 --> 00:26:31,240
You got a death wish?

717
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:38,160
You did the right thing.

718
00:26:38,550 --> 00:26:39,200
That Gangdao businessman

719
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,730
is staying here too, right?

720
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,130
I want to see him.

721
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:43,830
Yes, Du...

722
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:54,510
Du Zhaohui.

723
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,930
What are you trying to pull now?

724
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:58,680
Xia Xiaolan,

725
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,240
after getting kicked

726
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:00,880
by your friend earlier,

727
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,830
my head hasn't felt right.

728
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,620
I get dizzy when I stand up.

729
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,020
Excuse me for this.

730
00:27:07,010 --> 00:27:08,280
Could these two be

731
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:09,750
Mr. Kang Wei's family?

732
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:11,860
I'm Du Zhaohui.

733
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,300
You're Du Zhaohui?

734
00:27:18,350 --> 00:27:20,210
What is Du Chengrong of Gangdao's

735
00:27:20,550 --> 00:27:21,880
Chengrong Group to you?

736
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,680
He's my old... my daddy.

737
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,890
Then Lin Lizhen is your mother.

738
00:27:32,550 --> 00:27:33,240
You also have

739
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,550
a half-brother

740
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:36,110
named Du Zhaoji,

741
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:36,600
right?

742
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:38,160
Young Master.

743
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:40,030
Yes, Uncle.

744
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:41,930
Let me tell you.

745
00:27:43,440 --> 00:27:44,570
This is Shengcheng.

746
00:27:44,830 --> 00:27:46,630
If you've done something wrong,

747
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,850
you must take responsibility!

748
00:27:48,850 --> 00:27:49,880
I will, I will.

749
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:51,240
Of course, I'll take responsibility.

750
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:52,490
Medical bills, emotional distress—

751
00:27:52,490 --> 00:27:53,240
I'll cover everything.

752
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:54,640
So what if you have money?

753
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:56,920
You think money can fix everything?

754
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:58,350
You've misunderstood.

755
00:27:58,350 --> 00:27:59,240
I hit someone,

756
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:00,830
so I'll definitely take responsibility.

757
00:28:00,830 --> 00:28:01,590
Besides medical bills,

758
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,480
if there's anything else you need,

759
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:03,560
just tell me.

760
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:05,590
If anything happens to Kang Wei,

761
00:28:05,880 --> 00:28:06,540
I guarantee

762
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:11,000
your Du family won't be able to
bear the consequences!

763
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,480
Wei is awake.

764
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:13,510
I'll go get the doctor!

765
00:28:13,510 --> 00:28:13,920
Okay.

766
00:28:14,310 --> 00:28:15,040
Wei is awake.

767
00:28:16,010 --> 00:28:16,520
Wei!

768
00:28:16,550 --> 00:28:17,750
Let's get out of here.

769
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,530
Xiaolan,

770
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:23,880
let me take a look.

771
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:26,560
Are you feeling uncomfortable
anywhere else?

772
00:28:27,070 --> 00:28:27,920
I'm fine.

773
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,350
Does it hurt a lot?

774
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:45,350
Wei.

775
00:28:45,370 --> 00:28:46,040
Mom.

776
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:48,310
Where am I?

777
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:50,080
This is the hospital.

778
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,590
The patient's condition is stable.

779
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:53,830
He'll need time to recover.

780
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:54,790
But for the next couple of days,

781
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:56,250
avoid anything too solid—

782
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:57,590
stick mainly to a liquid diet.

783
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,240
Okay.

784
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:01,960
Second Uncle,

785
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:03,480
why are you here too?

786
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:04,680
Something this serious happened to you.

787
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,810
How could I not come?

788
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:07,310
If you feel unwell anywhere,

789
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,010
tell me.

790
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:10,890
For now, just focus on recovering.

791
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,160
Sis Bai,

792
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:14,880
where is Xiaolan?

793
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,230
She's fine.

794
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:18,400
Stop talking now.

795
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:20,030
Close your eyes

796
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:21,310
and get some rest.

797
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,480
My poor child.

798
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:29,880
Xia Xiaolan,

799
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,700
this is all your fault!

800
00:29:32,470 --> 00:29:33,960
If you hadn't wanted to
come to Shengcheng,

801
00:29:33,960 --> 00:29:35,880
Cheng and Wei wouldn't have come here.

802
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,550
If you hadn't insisted on doing business,

803
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:39,310
Wei wouldn't have gotten into an accident!

804
00:29:39,310 --> 00:29:39,880
Auntie,

805
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:41,070
I understand you're saying this

806
00:29:41,070 --> 00:29:42,270
because you're worried about Wei.

807
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:42,790
But what happened to Wei

808
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:44,880
really has nothing to do with Xiaolan!

809
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,270
Wei is already

810
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:47,400
an adult who can make

811
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,460
his own decisions.

812
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:49,070
Cheng...

813
00:29:49,070 --> 00:29:49,720
Auntie.

814
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:52,610
The business we're doing
is completely legitimate.

815
00:29:52,610 --> 00:29:53,940
Kang Wei's car accident

816
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,490
has nothing to do with that.

817
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:56,960
If you don't want him

818
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,480
staying in Shengcheng anymore,

819
00:29:58,480 --> 00:29:59,510
you can wait until he wakes up

820
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:01,110
and discuss it with him then.

821
00:30:01,350 --> 00:30:02,790
Arguing here right now

822
00:30:03,070 --> 00:30:04,350
won't help him at all.

823
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:05,190
You...

824
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:05,790
Yun.

825
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:07,930
I don't care.

826
00:30:08,410 --> 00:30:09,590
I'm going to arrange a transfer

827
00:30:09,590 --> 00:30:10,590
for Wei right now.

828
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:11,720
Auntie,

829
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:15,270
if you transfer him back to Jingcheng,

830
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,920
it'll be a long trip—

831
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,000
car and plane.

832
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:19,510
He just had surgery.

833
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:20,880
His body can't take it.

834
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:23,360
Why don't you wait a few days

835
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:26,240
until he recovers a bit
before taking him back?

836
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:28,040
Wei is a very stubborn child.

837
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:30,030
If he recovers,

838
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,700
he won't come back with me.

839
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:32,240
Yun,

840
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:33,350
I think...

841
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:35,360
the girl has a point.

842
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:39,040
Auntie,

843
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,170
don't worry.

844
00:30:40,690 --> 00:30:42,160
Since I'm the one
who talked you out of it,

845
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:44,260
I'll take responsibility for the outcome.

846
00:30:44,260 --> 00:30:45,330
When he recovers,

847
00:30:45,350 --> 00:30:46,880
if he refuses to go with you,

848
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,740
I'll kick him out the door myself!

849
00:30:48,900 --> 00:30:50,430
Du Zhaohui you saw just now—

850
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:52,610
I was the one who kicked him like that.

851
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:57,400
You girl...

852
00:30:57,830 --> 00:30:59,030
What's your name?

853
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,450
Bai Zhenzhu.

854
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:02,960
I used to run a stall at Renmin Bridge.

855
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:04,350
Now I've opened

856
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:06,350
a building materials shop of my own.

857
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:10,150
Alright then.

858
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:12,750
I'll listen to you.

859
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:15,210
We won't transfer him for now.

860
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,230
Okay.

861
00:31:17,070 --> 00:31:17,730
Zhou Cheng,

862
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:18,920
take Xiaolan back to her ward.

863
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:20,650
I'm going to get some hot water.

864
00:31:22,070 --> 00:31:22,750
Miss Bai!

865
00:31:23,510 --> 00:31:24,480
I'll go with you.

866
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:24,880
Okay.

867
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:28,390
Second Uncle,

868
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:30,000
then I'll take her...

869
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:30,330
Okay.

870
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,550
I'll go help them.

871
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:31,930
Okay.

872
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:33,790
Let's go.

873
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:36,280
Careful.

874
00:31:39,780 --> 00:31:40,300
Come on.

875
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:45,680
Come on.

876
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,600
Visiting hours are over.

877
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,360
Can I stay overnight?

878
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,160
Family members only.

879
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,240
Are you her family?

880
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,680
I... sort of am.

881
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:00,000
"Sort of?"

882
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:01,370
So you're not, then.

883
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,530
Come back tomorrow.

884
00:32:04,310 --> 00:32:04,960
It's okay.

885
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,550
Go back and rest.

886
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,040
You've had a long day too.

887
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:09,350
I'll be fine.

888
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:11,240
If you don't leave now,

889
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:13,590
the nurse might call the police

890
00:32:13,590 --> 00:32:15,320
to report you for harassing me.

891
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,570
Alright, I'm going.

892
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,440
I'll bring you breakfast tomorrow.

893
00:32:25,870 --> 00:32:26,830
Please leave now, sir.

894
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:27,750
The patient needs rest.

895
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:28,750
Okay. Rest well.

896
00:32:37,370 --> 00:32:38,000
Sis Bai,

897
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,640
thank you so much for today.

898
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,270
You don't have to

899
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,750
be so polite with me.

900
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:45,570
I've been thinking

901
00:32:45,790 --> 00:32:47,830
that Xiaolan hasn't been
doing well lately.

902
00:32:47,830 --> 00:32:49,000
Should we ask her mom

903
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:50,510
to come and keep her company?

904
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:52,310
Xiaolan asked me not to tell her mom.

905
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:53,440
She even specifically
called her mom earlier

906
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:55,480
and said she'd gone to Longcheng recently.

907
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:57,340
She doesn't want her mom to worry.

908
00:32:57,510 --> 00:32:58,880
Since she doesn't want us to tell,

909
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:00,110
let's not say anything.

910
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:01,710
I'll come by early tomorrow.

911
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:05,310
Second Uncle,

912
00:33:05,310 --> 00:33:06,510
l-let me walk you out.

913
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,340
No need.

914
00:33:07,350 --> 00:33:08,160
I can manage on my own.

915
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:09,110
It's fine, really. I'll walk you.

916
00:33:09,110 --> 00:33:10,070
Let's go together then.

917
00:33:10,070 --> 00:33:10,600
Let's go.

918
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:17,070
In this era, there aren't that many cars

919
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:18,790
on the streets of Shengcheng yet.

920
00:33:18,790 --> 00:33:20,070
A serious car accident

921
00:33:20,070 --> 00:33:21,440
is a rare occurrence.

922
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:23,440
Du Zhaohui's panic

923
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,840
didn't seem fake either.

924
00:33:26,550 --> 00:33:27,480
If it really was

925
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,880
just an accident...

926
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:38,050
Why is it a car crash again?

927
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:40,880
Why that same piercing sound again?

928
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:42,410
Could this be

929
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:44,750
fate warning me?

930
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:52,790
Zhou Cheng?

931
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:54,920
Why did you come back?

932
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:58,680
I didn't want to leave you alone

933
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,160
here.

934
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:04,590
Young Master,

935
00:34:04,590 --> 00:34:05,720
if you go back to Gangdao now,

936
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:07,310
won't you just hand Ms. Xia over

937
00:34:07,310 --> 00:34:07,880
to that Jerk Zhou?

938
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:09,440
Could you be any more stupid?

939
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,190
With Zhou here,

940
00:34:10,190 --> 00:34:11,449
I don't stand a chance.

941
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,760
What, should I stick around

942
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:14,690
and get beaten up by that Kang—

943
00:34:14,690 --> 00:34:15,889
whatever his name is?

944
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:17,870
But he was right about one thing.

945
00:34:18,630 --> 00:34:20,360
My old man doesn't only have me.

946
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:22,670
People in Gangdao are eyeing us hungrily.

947
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:23,670
They might take this opportunity

948
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:24,710
to stab me in the back.

949
00:34:24,710 --> 00:34:26,170
I should go back and check.

950
00:34:26,230 --> 00:34:27,150
Then what about Shengcheng?

951
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:27,760
Do we need to find someone...

952
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,820
Don't do anything.

953
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:31,550
That Kang guy is no ordinary person.

954
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:33,630
Just do whatever the traffic police say.

955
00:34:33,630 --> 00:34:34,630
First thing tomorrow morning,

956
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:35,880
have a lawyer come to the hospital.

957
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:36,960
Whatever they ask,

958
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:38,679
we'll agree—as long as it's legal.

959
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:39,010
Okay.

960
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:39,840
Got it.

961
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,380
I just went to check on Wei.

962
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:47,070
Second Uncle was really angry today.

963
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:49,000
If Wei's surgery hadn't gone well,

964
00:34:50,510 --> 00:34:51,320
I'm afraid...

965
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:53,420
Kang Wei always said

966
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:55,150
Second Uncle never paid him
much attention.

967
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:57,010
Seems that wasn't entirely true.

968
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:02,920
So, do you think

969
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,520
Du Zhaohui did it on purpose?

970
00:35:05,550 --> 00:35:06,350
Probably not.

971
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:08,710
He has no motive.

972
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:10,550
And he wouldn't be stupid enough

973
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:12,350
to commit a crime in Shengcheng.

974
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,170
I know he still likes you

975
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,330
and wants to pursue you.

976
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:20,390
You're so wonderful.

977
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:22,940
It's only natural for men to like you.

978
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:24,000
However,

979
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:26,230
I'll keep working hard to improve.

980
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:27,760
I won't give him an opening.

981
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:34,820
Well, that depends on

982
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:36,880
whether you're competitive enough.

983
00:35:42,140 --> 00:35:45,860
♪ I don't know when it started ♪

984
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:45,880
Why are you staring at me?

985
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:49,160
♪ But my world suddenly became bright ♪

986
00:35:48,150 --> 00:35:49,290
You're covered in injuries…

987
00:35:49,290 --> 00:35:52,970
♪ In the second our eyes met ♪

988
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:51,920
It must hurt.

989
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:56,160
♪ I knew it had to be you ♪

990
00:35:56,230 --> 00:35:56,820
Don't move.

991
00:35:56,820 --> 00:36:00,390
♪ Fireworks paint the sky tonight ♪

992
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:03,480
♪ Yet you'd rather stand in the rain ♪

993
00:36:01,110 --> 00:36:03,150
It doesn't matter
that you have injuries on your face.

994
00:36:03,150 --> 00:36:04,150
You're still beautiful.

995
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:07,480
♪ Every secret you keep inside ♪

996
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:08,200
You really know
how to make a girl feel better.

997
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:10,480
♪ I gather slowly, one by one ♪

998
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,510
What about your hand?

999
00:36:10,510 --> 00:36:16,400
♪ Countless times,
I've tried to tell you ♪

1000
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,780
Did the doctor check it properly?

1001
00:36:13,590 --> 00:36:14,440
Don't worry.

1002
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:15,880
They did a full check-up.

1003
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:16,510
I'm fine.

1004
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:17,800
Let me see.

1005
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:19,480
♪ Even if the world turned upside down ♪

1006
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,000
You're not feeling any discomfort, right?

1007
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:21,190
♪ I'd always find you ♪

1008
00:36:21,570 --> 00:36:24,540
♪ My beloved ♪

1009
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:24,470
Zhou Cheng...

1010
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:26,540
Don't move.

1011
00:36:26,620 --> 00:36:30,480
♪ I'd give anything just to see you ♪

1012
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,200
I just want to hold you like this.

1013
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:34,570
♪ I'd move heaven and earth for you ♪

1014
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:38,010
♪ I trust that time will lead me to you ♪

1015
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:40,040
♪ I can forget everything ♪

1016
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:39,320
Xiaolan.

1017
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:42,060
♪ Except your eyes ♪

1018
00:36:42,080 --> 00:36:45,790
♪ I see the moments we shared ♪

1019
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:43,000
I was so scared.

1020
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,070
I want to...

1021
00:36:45,810 --> 00:36:49,190
♪ I hear you calling out our vows ♪

1022
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,820
hold you like this,

1023
00:36:49,210 --> 00:36:53,100
♪ I believe, and I hope you do too ♪

1024
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,330
for as long as possible,

1025
00:36:52,230 --> 00:36:53,120
and never leave your side.

1026
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:54,540
♪ Whenever I see you ♪

1027
00:36:54,570 --> 00:36:57,950
♪ Our love echoes ♪

1028
00:37:12,630 --> 00:37:13,960
Granny Yu, you're back.

1029
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:15,400
Um...

1030
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:17,440
I made some turnip cake.

1031
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:19,700
Could you try it
and see if I made it right?

1032
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:23,800
Why isn't Xiaolan up yet?

1033
00:37:24,070 --> 00:37:25,200
I'll go check on her.

1034
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:27,960
Didn't she

1035
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:29,230
call yesterday and say

1036
00:37:29,490 --> 00:37:31,110
she was going to Longcheng for a few days

1037
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:32,840
to discuss the clothing store?

1038
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,680
Your memory is terrible.

1039
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:37,170
How will you
manage the shop for her later?

1040
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,840
There's no hope for you.

1041
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:43,150
I... I just forgot.

1042
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:45,880
She rarely goes on business trips
so suddenly.

1043
00:37:47,230 --> 00:37:49,430
Why did she go to Longcheng so suddenly?

1044
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:51,440
And stay there for several days?

1045
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:00,150
Alright.

1046
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,290
Go back quickly.

1047
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,710
If the nurse catches you,

1048
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:04,570
they won't let you visit anymore.

1049
00:38:31,110 --> 00:38:31,920
Don't worry.

1050
00:38:32,470 --> 00:38:33,400
It doesn't hurt.

1051
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:40,070
I'll head off then.

1052
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:41,280
Okay.

1053
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:44,070
I, uh...

1054
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:46,360
have to go to the court this morning.

1055
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,440
In the afternoon... uh...

1056
00:38:47,440 --> 00:38:48,670
I'll come over early if I can.

1057
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:50,000
Take care of yourself.

1058
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,370
Call Zhenzhu if you need anything.

1059
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,150
Be careful.

1060
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:57,200
I'm fine.

1061
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,230
About Wei's mom,

1062
00:39:03,230 --> 00:39:04,630
you don't need to worry too much either.

1063
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:05,550
She was just

1064
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:06,190
too anxious yesterday;

1065
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:08,050
that's why she said those things.

1066
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:09,760
Okay.

1067
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:10,690
Hurry and go.

1068
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,110
I'm off.

1069
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,250
Time for rounds!

1070
00:39:18,290 --> 00:39:19,350
Get down, get down.

1071
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:20,070
Quick.

1072
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,410
Alright, the nurse is gone.

1073
00:39:26,710 --> 00:39:28,510
Comrade Zhou Cheng, be careful.

1074
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,180
Then I'm going.

1075
00:39:34,110 --> 00:39:35,640
I'm really going this time.

1076
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:37,850
Bye-bye.

1077
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:41,490
Bye-bye.

1078
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,710
Am I overthinking?

1079
00:39:52,550 --> 00:39:53,550
Zhou Cheng...

1080
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:56,340
seems somehow different from usual.

1081
00:40:04,110 --> 00:40:05,360
I've been coming to the hospital
more often lately,

1082
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:07,550
picking up medicine for my mom
or taking her to get injections.

1083
00:40:07,550 --> 00:40:09,110
You're such a filial child.

1084
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:10,720
And so kind-hearted too.

1085
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:12,250
This is the ward.

1086
00:40:12,850 --> 00:40:13,180
Okay.

1087
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,650
Here, give me the thermos.

1088
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:21,030
Here, give me the fruit as well.

1089
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:21,760
Let me.

1090
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,550
Thank you.

1091
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:23,510
No problem, Auntie.

1092
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:24,150
I'll be going now.

1093
00:40:24,150 --> 00:40:24,480
Okay, okay.

1094
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,190
Goodbye, Auntie.

1095
00:40:25,190 --> 00:40:25,720
Goodbye.

1096
00:40:27,540 --> 00:40:28,490
Morning, Auntie.

1097
00:40:28,490 --> 00:40:29,550
Morning, Miss Bai!

1098
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:30,800
Who was that girl?

1099
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:32,550
I went to get food

1100
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:34,110
but couldn't find the place.

1101
00:40:34,110 --> 00:40:35,510
That child took me there

1102
00:40:35,510 --> 00:40:36,800
and brought me back.

1103
00:40:37,290 --> 00:40:38,190
I bought some fruit,

1104
00:40:38,190 --> 00:40:39,280
and she insisted on carrying it for me.

1105
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,550
She's such a kind girl.

1106
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,760
Why have you...

1107
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,000
come so early today?

1108
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:50,070
I came to bring breakfast
for the two of them.

1109
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,730
The hospital food isn't good.

1110
00:40:52,030 --> 00:40:53,070
Auntie, since you're here,

1111
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:55,070
I'll go bring breakfast to Xiaolan.

1112
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,540
Don't be in such a rush.

1113
00:40:56,590 --> 00:40:58,120
Let's eat together in a bit!

1114
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:58,780
Well...

1115
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:00,630
A-Are you done cleaning him up?

1116
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:01,710
Mom,

1117
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,200
you don't need to wipe me,

1118
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:05,110
or you'll rub my skin off.

1119
00:41:06,630 --> 00:41:07,800
What do you know?

1120
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:16,460
Senior.

1121
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:19,040
I've thought it over.

1122
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:22,410
That didn't look like an accident.

1123
00:41:22,590 --> 00:41:24,480
How could it be such a coincidence?

1124
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,920
Shi Kai and I just got a lead

1125
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,510
and were about to investigate

1126
00:41:26,510 --> 00:41:28,640
-the key information...
-Zhou Cheng!

1127
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:31,730
Zhou Cheng.

1128
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:34,320
Come with me to Shi Kai's hometown

1129
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,480
in a couple of days.

1130
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:39,280
His wife, child, and mother

1131
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:41,490
are all waiting for him.

1132
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,670
This is...

1133
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:51,140
some compensation from the firm.

1134
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:53,760
As for the case,

1135
00:41:54,230 --> 00:41:55,360
let's put it on hold.

1136
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,440
Wait for the results from the police

1137
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:57,510
and the court.

1138
00:41:58,440 --> 00:41:59,840
When we get back from Shi Kai's hometown,

1139
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:01,370
you should take a break too.

1140
00:42:01,630 --> 00:42:03,230
You've been busy for so long.

1141
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,670
Spend some time with your girlfriend.

1142
00:42:05,670 --> 00:42:06,110
Right?

1143
00:42:07,030 --> 00:42:08,090
Work is important,

1144
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:10,320
but family matters more.

1145
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:22,190
Not bad,

1146
00:43:22,480 --> 00:43:23,590
the hospital bed.

1147
00:43:26,030 --> 00:43:27,230
When did you get here?

1148
00:43:27,970 --> 00:43:29,630
I've been here for a while now,

1149
